  "body": "  Prove: There are no integers and such that .     We proceed by contradiction. So suppose there are integers and such that . So is even. We have seen that this implies that is even. So for some integer . Then . This in turn gives . But is even, and is odd, so these cannot be equal. Thus we have a contradiction, so there must not be any integers and such that .    "
